e fast and figure out how to get around the vast sewer system.\n\nYou\u2019ll need to use clever tactics to guide the lost rat, as it will react to your movements and actions. Will it follow your lead, or will it run away out of fear? It\u2019s all up to you.\n\nIt is time to enter the sewer.", "short_description": "You are a rat. Enter the sewer system and help a fellow rat escape what lurks within it."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.termsfeed.com/live/1b7bff2b-076c-44a2-b462-db150a651fff", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Bezbro Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://bezbrogames.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "411892083130028"}, {"id": "275629210202852"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "1394543634671740"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "226679486946564"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "226679486946564"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1690579800, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "226679486946564"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "6973435412757189", "version": "19.93"}, "id": "744776554061767", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary